title: The Show Is Divided On The Laurel Vs. Yanny Debate + Eddie Jr. Jr. Sings Along To Popular Songs
itunes:title: The Show Is Divided On The Laurel Vs. Yanny Debate + Eddie Jr. Jr. Sings Along To Popular Songs
description:
The big debate right now is an audio clip circulating the internet where some people are hearing the word "Laurel" and others hear the word "Yanny." The show is divided on it and debates what the clip actually says. Eddie brings audio of his 4-year-old son singing along to popular songs. Also, Bobby gives his top albums of 2018 so far.
